3. **Holonomic test**: pi(n) is NOT holonomic — new result, stronger than "not LRS."

4. **Short-interval explicit formula**: Confirms O(√x·polylog) optimum. No iteration help.

5. **Ono partition**: O(n²) per evaluation, CLOSED.
