## Synthesis of All 11 Experiments

| Experiment | Approach | Result | Barrier Hit |
|---|---|---|---|
| CRT | Modular reconstruction | π(x; q, a) as hard as π(x) | Circularity |
| Hierarchical Sieve | Fast-multipole for Φ | Recursion scales linearly with x | Equivalence |
| Spectral Compression | Compress zero sum | δ(n) needs 78% of Fourier coefficients for 99% | Info loss |
