    16	- **ML (Kolpakov-Rocke):** Maximum entropy argument proves ML learns smooth part only, not oscillatory correction.
    17	- **Ramanujan Library (ICLR 2025):** PSLQ on hypergraph of constants -- potentially applicable to delta(n) relations.
